author: Hypebeast (info@hypebeast.com)
title: Migos Head to Nigeria for Their "Call Casting" Video
text:
Migos are back with a new video for their song "Call Casting," a hard-hitting cut from their forthcoming project CULTURE which is anticipated to drop in the coming weeks. The Atlanta trio made their way overseas to Nigeria in the visual, sporting a healthy dose of iced out chains and vintage tees as they explore the country's stunning natural landscape before heading back to Lagos. The aforementioned city was also the site of a memorable Migos concert in December where the crowd went absolutely nuts to the trio's hit song "Bad & Boujee ." Check out the clip above and stay tuned for more updates regarding CULTURE on our site.
